In environment A : Type dom : Dom.t X : ∀ eqA : relation A, Equivalence eqA → ∀ R : relation A, PreOrder R → Prop Unable to unify "Equivalence (eq (dom₂:=?M2221))" with "∀ x : t A dom, (fix pointwise_lifting (op : binary_relation Prop) (l : Tlist) {struct l} : binary_relation (predicate l) := match l as l0 return (binary_relation (predicate l0)) with | Tnil => λ R R' : predicate Tnil, op R R' | Tcons A tl => λ R R' : predicate (Tcons A tl), ∀ x0 : A, pointwise_lifting op tl (R x0) (R' x0) end) iff (Tcons (t A dom) Tnil) (eq x) (relation_conjunction (incl (dom₂:=dom)) (flip (incl (dom₂:=dom))) x)".
